faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己得益上位就唔改個制度 輸撚左先黎屌個制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n改呢個制度真係會分裂啦 美國各州人口分佈差異極大 少至幾十萬人 多至幾千萬人既州都有 一改就對細州唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d78fc50f0f4811cfb7f2e5da2da191a0de5ba5b","tid":98391,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nClinton 贏 trump 2百萬張 popular vote <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係美國歷史以來贏普選票但落選總統最多的一屆</blockquote><br />\n選之前兩邊都同意呢個規則，嗰時唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人計過極限狀態得30%選票都可以贏添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2000都試過啦，戈爾贏幾十萬票，但布殊仔做總統，咁2008民主黨上返台又唔改過個制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己得益上位就唔改個制度 輸撚左先黎屌個制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n事實上trump自己選之前一路有屌<br />\n而家贏咗梗係則則膊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc081ca897670aaccf7496eb6c3ec94d40c4ff63","tid":98391,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:21:29.000Z","msg